{"tid":2108344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［聲討康怡婆婆］專業清算師：有任務想你地幫手做！","createTime":"2020-07-14T13:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T15:14:01.000Z","uid":22556,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d70a1e5338185389c5e73fdcb571af8b68af10eb","tid":2108344,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T13:00:34.000Z","msg":"【全城共憤！港鐵康怡管業處涉嫌欺負72歲婆婆張貼揮春！】<br />\n<br />\n根據蘋果日報跟進報導，港鐵康怡花園管業處被指針對及欺負婆婆，清算師團隊想問大家意見，我哋應唔應該出手相助？如果留言數目達10000個或以上，團隊會係星期五安排一鍵投訴，協助婆婆為業主討回公道！<br />\n<br />\n手足任務留言 &ldquo;一鍵投訴康怡花園欺負婆婆張貼揮春&rdquo;，同時tag傳媒、康怡相關群組及連登！<br />\n<br />\n另外，歡迎康怡業主PM爆料！ (H座某業委嘛！繼續爆料嚟！) <a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/finance/20200713/LSCMLKTXZE55FDQKTJXXNHR2IU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200713%2FLSCMLKTXZE55FDQKTJXXNHR2IU%2F&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuDUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=89d12dd8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200713%2FLSCMLKTXZE55FDQKTJXXNHR2IU%2F&h=36f300b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/finance/20200713/LSCMLKTXZE55FDQKTJXXNHR2IU/</a><br />\n<br />\n轉載請註明出處：專業清算師<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/revengehi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frevengehi&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuDUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=56b0ff8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/revengehi</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/revengehi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevengehi&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuDUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=3c817b84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/revengehi</a>"},{"pid":"a01e22684ad6b94dc7075f8cf382cab702bda68c","tid":2108344,"uid":264450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T13:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adf57517428001e3f42e947430d5